author_ssm: Marissa Hiller, with Charlie Morgan, 2015. Sophie Glidden-Lyon, 2016.
unittitle_ssm: Lindseth Collection of Alice in Wonderland Ephemera
abstract_ssm: The Lindseth Collection of Alice in Wonderland Ephemera comprises toys, auction catalogs, games, housewares, dolls, posters, books, vinyl sound discs and art relating to Alice in Wonderland collected by Dr. Lall Montgomery. This collection documents Alice in Wonderland in American popular culture.
